This repository contains an organized index, Chinese translations, and
companion scripts for declassified UAP/UFO materials released by the
U.S. government on May 8, 2026.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Source documents
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The original PDF, video, image, and metadata files referenced in this
repository are works of the U.S. federal government and are released
into the public domain under 17 U.S.C. § 105. They are NOT covered by
this license — they remain in the public domain and may be used freely
for any purpose, with no attribution required.

Original sources:
  • https://www.war.gov/medialink/ufo/release_1/
  • https://www.dvidshub.net/

