────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Disclaimer
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This repository is an unofficial, community-maintained index. The
maintainers make no claims about the authenticity, completeness, or
interpretation of any document. Translations are provided on a
best-effort basis; the English originals (collapsed inside <details>
blocks) are authoritative.
